public abstract class ViewElementBuilderSupport<T extends MutableViewElement,SELF extends ViewElementBuilder<T>> extends Object implements ViewElementBuilder<T>
Base class for a ViewElementBuilder of a MutableViewElement. Provides defaults functionality like configuring a custom templates or a set of post processors.
